-- Sesa Goa to Fund `Substantial' Part of Cairn India Acquisition With Cash
-- B y   A b h i s h e k   S h a n k e r
-- 2010-10-19T04:09:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-19/sesa-goa-to-fund-substantial-part-of-cairn-india-acquisition-with-cash.html
Sesa Goa Ltd. will fund a
substantial part of the purchase of a stake in Cairn India Ltd.
with cash, Managing Director P.K. Mukherjee said today in a
conference call.  To contact the reporter on this story:
